---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  current="how"
  title="How RRS Realty Group Works — Get Matched With a Local Agent"
  description="See how RRS Realty Group connects Southeast Wisconsin homeowners and buyers with vetted local real estate agents in three simple steps. Free and no obligation."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Simple process</p>
      <h1>How RRS Connects You With the Right Agent</h1>
      <p>No cold calls, no guesswork, no pressure. Here's exactly what happens from the moment you reach out.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:48px">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><h3>Tell Us About Your Move</h3><p>Fill out a short form with where your home is, your timeline, and whether you're buying or selling. The more detail you give, the better we can match you.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><h3>We Match You Locally</h3><p>We review your details and connect you with a vetted, licensed agent who actively works your area — someone who knows the neighborhood, the schools, and what homes are really selling for.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><h3>Talk on Your Terms</h3><p>Your matched agent reaches out to answer questions and walk you through next steps. There's never any obligation — you decide if and when to move forward.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section area">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Common questions</p>
        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Is It Really Free?</h3><p>Yes. Our matching service costs homeowners and buyers nothing. There's no fee to get connected with an agent.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Am I Obligated to Anything?</h3><p>No. Getting matched doesn't commit you to listing, buying, or hiring anyone. You're always free to walk away.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Who Are the Agents?</h3><p>Licensed Wisconsin real estate professionals who work in your specific area and have a track record we've reviewed.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>How Fast Will I Hear Back?</h3><p>We prioritize quick connections so you're not left waiting. Most homeowners hear from their matched agent promptly.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>What Areas Do You Cover?</h3><p>All eight counties of Southeast Wisconsin — from Milwaukee and Waukesha to Racine, Kenosha, and the surrounding communities.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>What If It's Not a Good Fit?</h3><p>Just let us know. The goal is the right match for you, not a forced one — there's no pressure to continue.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Ready to Get Matched?</h2>
      <p>It takes under two minutes and there's no obligation. Tell us about your move and we'll handle the rest.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/get-started/">Find my agent →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
